column2: select top # g.psfMag_u, g.psfMag_g, g.psfMag_u-g.psfMag_g as color, m.logMass from galaxy g join SpecObj s on s.bestObjID = g.objId join stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyDust m on m.specObjID = s.specObjID where g.psfMag_u-g.psfMag_g between # and # and m.logMass between # and # order by color desc
